5908.name: Red Soul Crystal: Stage 13
5908.description: Red Crystal that absorbs souls, stage 13. Special abilities can be applied to the weapon when absorbing certain amount of souls. Every time it is used, it consumes 26 of MP. However, the Soul Crystal of this stage absorbs souls by itself, so there is no need for using the Soul Crystal to monsters. Soul Crystal
